fields.title: Review the tests of the javascript array exercises 4/4
fields.body:
- [ ] Make sure the tests are working fine, add the necessary tests
- [ ] Make sure they're only using `let` instead of `var`
- [ ] Review the instructions, and make sure they're very explicit

Repository: https://github.com/4GeeksAcademy/javascript-arrays-exercises-tutorial

Exercises `20.1-Map-an-array` to `25-Techno-beat`
